<plot>Episode 1 When a lovely young singer enters a battle of the bands, she does so with hopes of super-stardom. Instead, she ends up being seen in the bathroom by a fellow contestant, and her darkest, largest secret is revealed! Now, this turn of events may turn her greatest rival into her greatest lover! Episode 2 She has the best of both worlds! Kaori doesn't know what happened in the past between her manager, Yuko, and the sexy singer, Saki, but now she's literally caught between them! When Saki invites Yuko and Kaori to her apartment along with the new singer, Sayaka, she has big plans for all four women. In this final chapter of Parade Parade, it's one last contest to satisfy Saki's grudge from three years ago, and the winner takes Kaori!</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?422918</url></doc>
